What does SEED mean?
I am new, and I don't understand!!

Seeds are people that have the WHOLE file (film in this case). Leechers are people downloading and having nothing or a part of the file. The more seeders the more people having a whole file = faster downloading!
Ni kan lika gärna skita i att ladda ner denna, den är helt kass en bit in på andra halvan av filmen, närmare bestämt 1.08.28 och framåt. Kvallen är hel värdelös.
Though the rip is good, the movie itself is totally lame!
